article_title: Contrary To The President's Claims, Obamacare Has Increased Healthcare Spending Growth

article_metadata.description: If this sort of thing is the best the president can say about ObamaCare, it is no wonder he just had to veto a bill repealing it.
article_metadata.author: Michael F. Cannon
